=Bio=

"Jarin Boonmathya is an independent thinker and researcher with the focus in the field of community development. He is the Advisor of the Graduate Volunteer program at Prince of Songkla University as well as an Advisor for the Thai Green Market Network’s Project to promote the use of organic produce in hospital’s kitchen."


